"{\"uid\": \"cyclingnews.com-news-get-the-drift-olympic-mountain-bike-racers-worry-about-gravel-on-man-made-paris-course\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Pieterse, Pidcock, Richards and Schurter weigh in on the man-made Elancourt Hill course  When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.Here's how it works.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 68, \"end\": 77, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elancourt\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are now subscribed  Your newsletter sign-up was successful  TheParis Olympic Gamesget underway this weekend with the women's and men's Mountain Bike Cross-country events taking place on a former landfill.\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top competitors were mixed in their assessment of the Elancourt Hill course after their training runs this week, noting the loose gravel and fully man-made course differs from what inspired mountain biking as a sport.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elancourt\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former Olympic champion Nino Schurter (Switzerland) voiced a unanimous assessment of the course.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nino_Schurter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nino Schurter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nino_Schurter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nino_Schurter\"}, {\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9999901086942258, \"rank\": 9.891333494334377e-06, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's slippery, it's quite loose and quite wide.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you go fast it's super slippery,\\\" Schurter said.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope the gravel still goes a bit to the side and makes it less loose everywhere.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can feel there was no mountain biking before and it's 100% man-made, like we saw in London and in Rio.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999990050128, \"rank\": 9.553688581531483e-10, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.828945896634137, \"rank\": 0.20635134820498935, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It could be a bit more natural, but in general, it's nice.\\\"\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The topDutch hopeful Puck Pietersealready did a full preview of the course last year ahead of the test event, so she knew what to expect but also noted the dry nature of the circuit will force riders to be comfortable with a little drift in the turns.\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1202, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_puck\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.182633127012339e-21, \"text\": \"Puck\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_puck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_puck\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's good.\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, we already had the chance to familiarise with the course and race here.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have made some small adjustments, but for the main part it's the same,\\\" Pieterse said.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of gravel, which is slippery, especially in the corners, so you have to be careful.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a course in which you have to be able to take a lot of speed into the corners and you should not be afraid to drift a little on the slippery surface.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The technical parts come quickly after each other but it's not such a long lap and there is no long three- to four-minute climb because all climbs are interrupted with little things,\\\" she said, adding, \\\"You have to be good on any course.\\\"\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pieterse expectedPauline Ferrand Pr\\u00e9votto be the top contender on her home turf.\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's in her home country, she's the top favourite, so that will put the pressure on, but it can also give her wings.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will find out on Sunday.\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel as if I did everything I could, so that gives me a lot of confidence.\\\"\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The British ridersTom Pidcock- one of the topmen's Olympic MTB favouritesas defending champion - and Evie Richards were not as bullish about the course, with Pidcock giving quite a blunt assessment.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2534, \"end\": 2541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9996778861631758, \"rank\": 0.0003221232572869422, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2631, \"end\": 2644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evie_Richards\", \"score\": 0.9999999329952538, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evie Richards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evie_Richards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evie_Richards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not the best course in the world but it's the same for everyone,\\\" Pidcock said.\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's bland and I think they could have done a better job of making a more mountain bike course.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love mountain biking for the reasons that drive us to enjoy it.\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the courses you get to ride, the places you get to go to.\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 3045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When you just gravel over a nice hillside, it's not really mountain biking.\\\"\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pidcock and Richards agreed that the course is less tactical than the ones they encounter during the season.\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3232, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is not much thinking to go into either.\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's kind of one line you just go down,\\\" Pidcock said.\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is just one line.\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Normally you can choose different lines,\\\" Richards said before adding, \\\"It's still technical because they have got lots of cool features, drops and jumps, but it's man-made.\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just one line, and you race that line.\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's probably easier to learn, but just less choices when you come to race.\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think they have done the best they have done.\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being as close as Paris, it's not the easiest thing to just pop up a mountain bike course anywhere.\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3724, \"end\": 3729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.433186762568366e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I was a designer, I'd like a lot more natural features rather than man-made.\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I think we normally see that at the Olympic Games, it's normally a bit of a different course than what we'd normally race at World Cups.\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 4028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are normally in the Alps, somewhere, somewhere in a nice ski resort and this is super close to the city centre.\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think they have done the best job of what they can do.\\\"\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dull course aside, Richards is excited to represent Britain at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 4203, \"to\": 4284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4255, \"end\": 4262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9987631121448104, \"rank\": 0.0012384195265210997, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics is all I ever dreamt of and that's why I got into sport.\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since the age of six, it was all I wanted to do.\", \"from\": 4357, \"to\": 4405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not just for me, but for my family, for my grandparents, it's what we have all ever dreamt of.\", \"from\": 4406, \"to\": 4500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not just my dream, it's all my family's dream come true.\", \"from\": 4501, \"to\": 4562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They will all be coming out to watch.\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing feels quite like representing your country, especially at the Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 4601, \"to\": 4678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get unlimited access to all of our coverage of the 2024 Olympic Games - including breaking news and analysis reported by our journalists on the ground from every event across road, mountain bike, track and BMX racing as it happens and more.Find out more.\", \"from\": 4680, \"to\": 4934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4886, \"end\": 4896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\", \"score\": 0.9999949500984436, \"rank\": 5.04992693392933e-06, \"text\": \"BMX racing\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura Weislo is aCyclingnewsveteran of 20 years.\", \"from\": 4936, \"to\": 4984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4936, \"end\": 4941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"score\": 0.9834295228599989, \"rank\": 0.016849675648240636, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having joined in 2006, Laura extensively covered the Operacion Puerto doping scandal, the years-long conflict between the UCI and the Tour de France organisers ASO over the creation of the WorldTour, and the downfall of Lance Armstrong and his lifetime ban for doping.\", \"from\": 4985, \"to\": 5253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5008, \"end\": 5013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"score\": 0.9834295228599989, \"rank\": 0.016849675648240636, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\"}, {\"begin\": 5038, \"end\": 5054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Operaci\\u00f3n_Puerto_doping_case\", \"score\": 0.9999999997394298, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Operacion Puerto\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Operaci\\u00f3n_Puerto_doping_case\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Operaci\\u00f3n_Puerto_doping_case\"}, {\"begin\": 5107, \"end\": 5110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6630209532566197e-16, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}, {\"begin\": 5119, \"end\": 5133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2486362327745973e-14, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 5145, \"end\": 5148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amaury_Sport_Organisation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1477202300581742e-23, \"text\": \"ASO\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amaury_Sport_Organisation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amaury_Sport_Organisation\"}, {\"begin\": 5205, \"end\": 5220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.076878180504672e-62, \"text\": \"Lance Armstrong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Managing Editor, Laura coordinates coverage for North American events and global news.\", \"from\": 5254, \"to\": 5343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5274, \"end\": 5279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"score\": 0.9834295228599989, \"rank\": 0.016849675648240636, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\"}, {\"begin\": 5311, \"end\": 5319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999905535333, \"rank\": 6.995609406913915e-09, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cyclingnews is part of Future plc, an international media group and leading digital publisher.Visit our corporate site.\", \"from\": 5345, \"to\": 5464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5345, \"end\": 5356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cyclingnews\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\"}, {\"begin\": 5368, \"end\": 5378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Future plc\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 Future Publishing Limited Quay House, The Ambury, Bath BA1 1UA.\", \"from\": 5466, \"to\": 5531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5468, \"end\": 5485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.752711942237814e-21, \"text\": \"Future Publishing\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\"}, {\"begin\": 5499, \"end\": 5504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"score\": 0.9907959611942927, \"rank\": 0.009289524463792737, \"text\": \"House\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 5532, \"to\": 5552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"England and Wales company registration number 2008885.\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5553, \"end\": 5560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\", \"score\": 0.9946288563101952, \"rank\": 0.0026801593735827885, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\"}, {\"begin\": 5565, \"end\": 5570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Wales\", \"score\": 0.9639718850569697, \"rank\": 0.03735661441738398, \"text\": \"Wales\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Wales\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please login or signup to comment  Please wait...\", \"from\": 5609, \"to\": 5658, \"entities\": []}]}"